{"tid":2293274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警隊副指揮官林華平警署警長認左係自己指示用催淚彈射擊政治異見者身體","createTime":"2020-11-20T06:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T08:24:06.000Z","uid":26770,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"615f465b28bdc9776170f9c94c8ee2df3267ac87","tid":2293274,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/GNQC5UJHEVEPXNPLAXKZEJVXMI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FGNQC5UJHEVEPXNPLAXKZEJVXMI%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=f13d4b07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FGNQC5UJHEVEPXNPLAXKZEJVXMI%2F&h=d0323477\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/GNQC5UJHEVEPXNPLAXKZEJVXMI/</a><br />\n科技大學男生周梓樂去年11月4日凌晨於將軍澳警民衝突中，在尚德邨停車場墮樓昏迷，留醫5天後不治，終年22歲。東九龍衝鋒隊第1小隊副指揮官、警署警長林華平出席死因研訊時提及，當時他曾警告示威者不要再擲物，其小隊中有警長遂自行決定發射三枚催淚彈。林華平更謂：<strong>「如果係要我叫fire呢，就會係十幾發子彈咁樣打㗎喇。」</strong>"},{"pid":"b5681d62773665687cd8acd536cf99f7ea5637b9","tid":2293274,"uid":19640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:33:38.000Z","msg":"好人早死，賤狗當道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfdb89f866e1c5caf5317c6781ecebdbf15e0a6","tid":2293274,"uid":11447,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:34:38.000Z","msg":"俾啲弱智嘅揸武器真係好危險"},{"pid":"b6c99b3810a8f138f1673e07d0ac364b3d1468d3","tid":2293274,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:35:03.000Z","msg":"1催淚彈實際係裝載催淚性刺激劑的非致命性<strong>化學武器</strong><br />\n根本唔需要同一地方打十幾發已經能夠控制現場<br />\n<br />\n當子彈打就讀證明大量異見者/市民中催淚彈重傷絕不是意外<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">係香港畜牲警希望示威者殘廢/死亡而故意瞄準</span></span>"},{"pid":"672cf8bd334929b622b15cef5f21ca41383930fa","tid":2293274,"uid":121197,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"